    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你接受了艾德·骷髅的邀请来尝试他的“令人惊叹的”电子游戏，但你很快意识到并非一切都按计划进行。他的游戏看起来缺乏灵感，而且绝对不好玩……请毫不犹豫地指出这一点。然而，带着永远存在的骷髅微笑的艾德并没有放弃：他增加了新的挑战，让怪物变得更可怕（或者至少他尝试过），并试图将你的体验变成独特的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/636d9fc18f9329008a286de10703f1dc.poster.avif?t=1755370626\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/636d9fc18f9329008a286de10703f1dc.webm?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/636d9fc18f9329008a286de10703f1dc.mp4?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但他并不总是骷髅，而骷髅脸会尝试吓到你到死你必须克服挑战，使用骷髅手枪击败可怕的怪物，并用骷髅解决简单的谜题，在一个关卡和另一个关卡之间，你将扮演艾德的角色，发现他被困在自己的游戏中的神秘故事.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃离巨大的尖叫骷髅..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/1bb5be730f1d496321417d7ef8033bca.poster.avif?t=1755370626\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/1bb5be730f1d496321417d7ef8033bca.webm?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/1bb5be730f1d496321417d7ef8033bca.mp4?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用骷髅手枪杀死可怕的可怕生物..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/3f040c378e03334b40c0eedef67880c6.poster.avif?t=1755370626\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/3f040c378e03334b40c0eedef67880c6.webm?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/3f040c378e03334b40c0eedef67880c6.mp4?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用头骨解决谜题..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/9bde59a49b00940ce6d108617c79ad3d.poster.avif?t=1755370626\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/9bde59a49b00940ce6d108617c79ad3d.webm?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/9bde59a49b00940ce6d108617c79ad3d.mp4?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 告诉 Edd Skeleton 他的游戏很糟糕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 害怕吧尖叫的头骨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 与骷髅一起参与奇异的场景和情境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 探索艾德骷髅的神秘故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 开发者一个拥有虚幻引擎的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/965ccd195ae3edcec0bd8803416ea607.poster.avif?t=1755370626\" width=390 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/965ccd195ae3edcec0bd8803416ea607.webm?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160840/extras/965ccd195ae3edcec0bd8803416ea607.mp4?t=1755370626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
